Substance bounds — the deterministic gate `gate:plan_ok` rejects anything
below them and re-dispatches you with the violation list:

- `beats` ≥ 3 entries, one per EDL beat, in EDL order.
- For every interior beat boundary (n-1 transitions for n beats), there
